Section.name: About Sanketika Vidya Parishad Engineering College
Section.description:
Sanketika Vidya Parishad Engineering College was established in 2003-2004 on Chennai- Kolkata NH-5 in the Visakhapatnam district of Andhra Pradesh. The campus is full of greeneries and is located in a scenic environment, with a backdrop of hills. The college is nearby to the main city and takes about 15 minutes to reach it from the RTC Complex. The college is well connected by the city buses.
